## claim tree

```
claim 1 (method - independent)
├── claim 2 (depends on 1)
├── claim 3 (depends on 1)
└── claim 4 (depends on 2)

claim 5 (system - independent)
├── claim 6 (depends on 5)
└── claim 7 (depends on 5)
```

